Add chicken to large nonstick skillet sprayed with cooking spray; cook 3 min. on each side. Add gravy to skillet; cook 5 min. or until chicken is cooked through. Meanwhile, combine stuffing mix and water. Spoon stuffing over chicken; cover. Cook 5 min. or until heated through. Place each stuffing topped chicken breast on 1 bread slice. Top with gravy from skillet. Serve with hot cooked peas.